{"word":"G4909 - συνευδοκέω - syneudokéō - soon-yoo-dok-eh'-o - Allow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνευδοκέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syneudokéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-yoo-dok-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Allow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உடன்படு, சம்மதி, பிரியப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be pleased together with, to approve together"},{"paragraph":"2. to be pleased at the same time with, consent, agree to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2106 - εὐδοκέω - eudokéō - yoo-dok-eh'-o/2106\">G2106</a>; to <i>think well of in common</i>, that is, <i>assent</i> to, <i>feel gratified with:</i> - allow, assent, be pleased, have pleasure.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}